By: MMAjunkie Staff | May 31, 2017 7:15 am

English heavyweight James Mulheron will make his promotional debut at UFC Fight Night 113.

Officials today announced Mulheron (11-1 MMA, 0-0 UFC) has replaced Mark Godbeer (12-3 MMA, 1-1 UFC) and is now slated to fight fellow promotional newcomer Justin Willis (4-1 MMA, 0-0 UFC) at the summer
